---
const proofItems = [
  {
    title: "Payment integrations",
    body: "Barclays, Worldpay and Stripe, taking real money every day.",
  },
  {
    title: "Retail EPOS & stock systems",
    body: "Tills, stock feeds and product data, kept in sync so the shelf and the website agree.",
  },
  {
    title: "Multi-storefront e-commerce",
    body: "Five storefronts run from one stack: online shops, CMS builds, product data and the SEO in front of it.",
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-paper-deep">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <h2 class="reveal font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-moss uppercase">
      Track record
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal mt-6 max-w-2xl font-display text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
      Built, and <em class="text-moss">running today</em>.
    </p>
    <dl class="mt-12 border-t border-ink/15">
      {
        proofItems.map((item) => (
          <div class="reveal grid gap-2 border-b border-ink/15 py-7 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_1.6fr] sm:gap-10">
            <dt class="font-display text-xl font-medium tracking-tight">
              {item.title}
            </dt>
            <dd class="leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">{item.body}</dd>
          </div>
        ))
      }
      <div class="reveal grid gap-2 border-b border-ink/15 py-7 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_1.6fr] sm:gap-10">
        <dt class="font-display text-xl font-medium tracking-tight">
          Software of my own
        </dt>
        <dd class="leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
          <a
            href="https://www.whatcable.uk"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-moss underline decoration-stone underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:text-moss-deep"
          >
            WhatCable
          </a>, a Mac app with paying customers worldwide. Designed, built,
          sold and supported by one person. When I say I stick around after
          launch, this is what that looks like.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
